scene.message:
{nl}
We've got a time limit, so if{nl}
we don't cut it off at some{nl}
point{waitkey}we could be in trouble.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I've gained a little{nl}
respect for you in our battles{nl}
so far. You're strong.{waitkey}{clearbox}And so... if I may put it to{nl}
you, once we beat "the Snow{nl}
Queen," when I go to save{nl}
Inaba,{waitkey}{clearbox}would you come along? I want{nl}
every fighter I can get. I{nl}
won't force it, of course...

Brown: Treasure chests! They{nl}
really are great!! Aaah!!{nl}
Chests!!{waitkey}Plenty of folks know the{nl}
word, but{waitkey}{clearbox}folks who've actually seen,{nl}
touched, or opened one are{nl}
few and far between!{waitkey}{ret}
